    "causal_summary": "The deep-research iteration cycle is itself a retrieval loop, but it threads forward in the \"reactive, reconstruct-cold\" mode, each iteration rebuilding its working set from the reducer's distilled snapshot rather than carrying its own prior thread, and the \"next focus\" it pursues is whatever free-text the previous iteration hand-wrote, not a function of what that iteration actually found",
